<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help - The Proving Grounds</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/provinggrounds/css/terminal.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terminal">
        <div class="ascii-box">
<pre>
===============================================
              HELP FILE
       The Proving Grounds BBS
===============================================
</pre>
        </div>

        <h2>Welcome to The Proving Grounds!</h2>
        <p>A fantasy BBS adventure where you can fight monsters,
battle other users, explore dungeons, and become the most
powerful warrior in the realm!</p>

        <h3>Getting Started</h3>
        <p>As a new character, you start at Level 1 with basic
equipment. Your goal is to gain experience by fighting
monsters in the Dungeon, then level up and acquire better
equipment from the stores.</p>

        <h3>Combat</h3>
        <p>- <strong>Dungeon:</strong> Fight monsters for gold and experience
- <strong>Proving Grounds:</strong> Battle other users for glory
- <strong>Corridor of Death:</strong> Deadly challenges for the brave
- <strong>Castle Attack:</strong> Raid the castle for treasures</p>

        <h3>Stores</h3>
        <p>Visit the Bazaar to purchase:
- <strong>Weapons:</strong> Increase your attack power
- <strong>Armor:</strong> Increase your defense
- <strong>Spells:</strong> Learn magical abilities
- <strong>Healing:</strong> Restore HP and Power
- <strong>Food:</strong> Required for survival</p>

        <h3>Banking</h3>
        <p>Use the Castle Treasury to store gold safely. Gold in
the bank cannot be stolen or lost when you die.</p>

        <h3>Jousting</h3>
        <p>Visit The Proving Downs to joust against other users
in mounted combat. Win gold and improve your jousting record!</p>

        <h3>Gambling</h3>
        <p>Test your luck at:
- Slot Machines (3, 4, or 5 wheels)
- Blackjack
- Roulette
- Russian Roulette (DANGER!)</p>

        <h3>Message Boards</h3>
        <p>Communicate with other users via the message boards.
Read announcements, share strategies, and make allies.</p>

        <h3>Daily Limits</h3>
        <p>You have a limited number of calls (logins) per day
and limited time per session. Use them wisely!</p>

        <h3>Levels</h3>
        <p>There are 100 levels to achieve, from "Low-Life Scum"
to "Immortal Timelord". Each level increases your stats
and unlocks access to better equipment.</p>

        <div class="menu" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <span class="menu-key">&lt;</span>
                <a href="/provinggrounds/main">Return to Main Menu</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-bar">
            <span>[<%= user.name %>]</span>
            <span>Level: <%= user.level %></span>
            <span>Gold: <%= user.gold %></span>
            <span>HP: <%= user.hp %>/<%= user.max_hp %></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/provinggrounds/js/terminal.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
